query:
INSERT INTO metrics_bakers (
              block_height,
              total_bakers_added,
              total_bakers_removed
            )
            SELECT
              $1,
              total_bakers_added + $2,
              total_bakers_removed + $3
            FROM (
              SELECT *
              FROM metrics_bakers
              ORDER BY block_height DESC
              LIMIT 1
            )
